properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 8 at 5:11PM PST until January 10 at 3:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph, except
isolated gusts to 60 mph at times near Montecito Hills.

* WHERE...Santa Barbara County Mountains.

* WHEN...Until 3 AM PST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will make driving difficult including
Highway 154, especially for high profile vehicles.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strongest winds in the Santa Ynez mountains
and adjacent foothills.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM PST FRIDAY
